The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week program designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. It covers essential topics like Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Students participate in three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16. The courses are available in both English and Spanish, and no prior experience is required. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. For more information, visit: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop